{"tid":631877,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"超高校級的將棋手！日本女流棋士香川愛生COS《彈丸論破》七海千秋！","createTime":"2018-04-17T01:31:03.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-17T07:57:01.000Z","uid":55628,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"f35c38ff9ad81b6135b123df07eaa2531ba135ee","tid":631877,"uid":55628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-17T01:31:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://imgur.com/KFsquWZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgur.com%2FKFsquWZ.jpg&h=72e74186&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n以往動畫、漫畫算是亞文化領域的作品，但現在動畫、漫畫隨著觀眾和讀者的成長已逐漸走向主流文化，像日本副首相麻生太郎就曾經被媒體目擊到閱讀《薔薇少女》漫畫，現今各行各業中都有一些傑出精英人物喜歡熱愛動畫、漫畫、遊戲。而在4月1日愚人節當天，曾經獲得過日本將棋界女流王將頭銜，與日高里菜一起做《龍王的工作》動畫每話感想戰的女流棋士香川愛生就曬出了自己《彈丸論破》七海千秋COS照，這是位超高校級的女流棋士！<br />\n<img src=\"https://imgur.com/dRJlFw8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgur.com%2FdRJlFw8.jpg&h=e2b0d8e3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n香川愛生是一位15歲就成為職業女流棋士的日本將棋界新秀，在2011年高中三年級時還為了學業暫時停止一年的棋士活動，在2012年復歸棋壇後，於2013年、2014年連續兩年獲得了女流王將頭銜，不過在2015年失去頭銜，目前作為現役女流將棋棋士，香川愛生也在努力重新取回女流王將頭銜。除了下棋外，香川愛生由於其外貌，被一部分將棋愛好者稱之為「將棋界的渡邊麻友」，在電視、網路媒體上，香川愛生也經常會擔任將棋對局解說，同時她本人也是日本將棋史上第一位以女流棋士的身份擔任一般頭銜戰對局記錄員（第38期棋王戰第二局）。<br />\n<img src=\"https://imgur.com/t6GbG6l.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgur.com%2Ft6GbG6l.jpg&h=71d6ffe9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n而在私生活中，香川愛生很喜歡遊戲並與知名遊戲雜誌《Fami通》交情不淺，還在這本雜誌上有自己的專欄連載，而且Fami通前總編的兒子與香川愛生在小學和初中都是同學。這次香川愛生COS的《彈丸論破》七海千秋獲得了小高和剛的高度評價，而且香川愛生也說自己是《彈丸論破》遊戲的忠實粉絲，小高與《彈丸論破》粉絲對自己COS照的高評價讓她確信這個世界是充滿希望的，在相關評論中也有網友喊出如果《龍王的工作》真人化的話，香川愛生絕對適合扮演空銀子！<br />\n<img src=\"https://imgur.com/dQMEUqr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgur.com%2FdQMEUqr.jpg&h=d1ed71b4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n香川愛生Instagram：<a href=\"https://t.co/6zjSDRh7by\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2F6zjSDRh7by&d=tW9yB1Mad%2BNiUHAfO6zkXsP%2FddU7lKBqZb2OVh9Tir8%3D&h=410a0716\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.co/6zjSDRh7by</a><br />\n汁：<a href=\"https://gamer.com.tw/forum/C.php?bsn=60076&amp;page=&amp;snA=4480347&amp;last=\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgamer.com.tw%2Fforum%2FC.php%3Fbsn%3D60076%26page%3D%26snA%3D4480347%26last%3D&d=tW9yB1Mad%2BNiUHAfO6zkXsP%2FddU7lKBqZb2OVh9Tir8%3D&h=f3f2bdea\" target=\"_blank\">https://gamer.com.tw/forum/C.php?bsn=60076&amp;page=&amp;snA=4480347&amp;last=</a>"},{"pid":"89fe03af8f98c62e76820f137c7ad9815371c35c","tid":631877,"uid":8307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-17T01:33:11.000Z","msg":"一二三<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4070f004cd75d99a4b8020a9b8e1b83d74d22d9","tid":631877,"uid":39840,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"89fe03af8f98c62e76820f137c7ad9815371c35c","tid":631877,"uid":8307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-17T01:33:11.000Z","msg":"一二三<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-17T01:35:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/w3ui2pF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fw3ui2pF.jpg&h=4b31730f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"10017e0f4e8022478d47873daab8e1b9dd48a7d7","tid":631877,"uid":93394,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f4070f004cd75d99a4b8020a9b8e1b83d74d22d9","tid":631877,"uid":39840,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"89fe03af8f98c62e76820f137c7ad9815371c35c","tid":631877,"uid":8307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-17T01:33:11.000Z","msg":"一二三<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-17T01:35:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/w3ui2pF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fw3ui2pF.jpg&h=4b31730f&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-17T01:42:44.000Z","msg":"仲有人叫三四<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d39caa